{"tid":1804291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黃色經濟圈】下一步, 就係要統計同分配我地嘅消費力","createTime":"2019-12-31T01:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T04:06:45.000Z","uid":71034,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dccc544324fd4fe0195fcc3d6bffd3a6680307b2","tid":1804291,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:29:10.000Z","msg":"依排政府不停想打壓黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係又有幾多人有諗過依個經濟圈究竟有幾強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解佢地咁撚驚?政府已經推算到經濟圈嘅威力<br />\n<br />\n假設200萬人入面得100萬人有工翻, 而佢地每月基本消費最少有5000蚊, 保守估計依到都有成50億<br />\n當然啦一個成年人每月邊會淨係洗5000蚊咁少, 所以50億只係一個非常保守嘅數字, 都仲未計另外個100萬人其實都會消費<br />\n<br />\n我地每個月最少可以令到藍色經濟圈無左50億營業額<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係依50億係咪真係會流得哂落去黃色經濟圈? 我可以話比你聽現階段係無可能<br />\n<br />\n點解? 就係因為我地無好好分配我地手頭上嘅消費力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據openrice 入面hker2019 收錄嘅黃店總數量係1241間, 假設50億入面得10億係飲食上嘅消費, 平均分配嘅話每間係會有80萬營業額<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係大家打開個ig 留意下身邊嘅朋友, 都會發現佢地來來去去唔係幫襯龍門就幫襯光榮<br />\n<br />\n我真心呼籲大家唔好撚再理嗰啲話xxx餐廳係偽黃嗰啲post, 總之入得條list 嘅就幫襯得<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以將自己手頭上嘅消費力好好咁分配, 例如港島 九龍同新界都各揀一間出黎幫襯, 不論偽唔偽黃都幫襯左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有1月1記住出黎遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcc3c54d12c9f629a61e52fe137c2b62ddb08e8","tid":1804291,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:30:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16636ca0ecc9c5ea128fdc36375a8c1c6d29baf6","tid":1804291,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:31:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2542030dab949a6ec6ac9d14be7a13a1230bc494","tid":1804291,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:32:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"938ce911b8544653e2c5c96d17b759211171f701","tid":1804291,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:33:07.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日踏入2020年，懇求大家去元旦遊行前睇一睇「七一立法會宣言」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3e311c776050622bc283f9cf6d9ace8b51125d7b","tid":1804291,"uid":94069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:33:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"706a36172c1d2c1e36c725f09437ae3111a108d8","tid":1804291,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:33:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d84cab43dead2ff1940fc0d334ecd15de400e457","tid":1804291,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:33:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"204fc78157430e102985df5698326fb042bffe5f","tid":1804291,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:35:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e18c7b51f9cbf9b2fd60f24d59f4b198d0bbf89","tid":1804291,"uid":88133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:35:51.000Z","msg":"搞大個餅先最有力量去抗衡紅色圈<br />\n而唔係又分黨分派<br />\n唔可以越黎越高標準<br />\n吸引更多資金流入黃色經濟體先有用"},{"pid":"3dc41588e962c43fa8c0db00ac876f168f527c82","tid":1804291,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e18c7b51f9cbf9b2fd60f24d59f4b198d0bbf89","tid":1804291,"uid":88133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:35:51.000Z","msg":"搞大個餅先最有力量去抗衡紅色圈<br />\n而唔係又分黨分派<br />\n唔可以越黎越高標準<br />\n吸引更多資金流入黃色經濟體先有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:38:18.000Z","msg":"係, 依家真係唔適合討論邊間xxx餐廳究竟偽唔偽黃, 咁樣只會嚇怕其他想加入嘅餐廳"},{"pid":"f0f7c553f9f6631b340b23a14bdfe9b00e5a8327","tid":1804291,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:39:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e036a5acfd536ce6d76929b5cab22e5753861f5","tid":