19/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n簽完share條link去tg"},{"pid":"ef9818fd5253c8bee90ddb9c4983562aeb910bf2","tid":1804291,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:42:44.000Z","msg":"唔好下下都去同一兩間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd17c3e61df465655c77b98bccd1c4de0a5fd36","tid":1804291,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:43:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢個計法太求銀祈<br />\n當average一日食一餐黃店<br />\n60X30都得1800<br />\n要計就精準啲用埋問卷<br />\n報大數打飛機把撚<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"c444594022893058d055bcf846fca19be541caf6","tid":1804291,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fd17c3e61df465655c77b98bccd1c4de0a5fd36","tid":1804291,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:43:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢個計法太求銀祈<br />\n當average一日食一餐黃店<br />\n60X30都得1800<br />\n要計就精準啲用埋問卷<br />\n報大數打飛機把撚<br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飲食方面, 我上面用左1000黎計咋, 咁都報大數??"},{"pid":"d4b9ce44f2fc09496c5a18f46b78da90019ea886","tid":1804291,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:49:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d092671935ead4314efd8bf78a372957ceb3db5","tid":1804291,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:50:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"768ea3d627870e7f09ab71aa327f6614a05e2254","tid":1804291,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:51:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e79b0e29eb27d46d2796885265cd478bae17e20","tid":1804291,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:58:28.000Z","msg":"都係睇區內有邊間黃店<br />\n間間都試下 順便自己心入面俾分<br />\n有文宣會加 用支那寶會減<br />\n嘢食好唔好食 服務點樣<br />\n唔會特別幫襯死一間<br />\n利申：好憎排隊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上見有人想搞聯盟<br />\n我希望唔好搞大台<br />\n我覺得應該由每區內黃店自己組<br />\n組完可能做啲合作聯乘優惠互相推廣<br />\n而唔係我地好似有人逼佢地要點做"},{"pid":"c387c2d9a02878e460399381571a0c7a60234b5d","tid":1804291,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:00:44.000Z","msg":"新手，打卡撚先去龍門，光榮"},{"pid":"8a3dd1f8c0114d3d329c6f5df53a7490e2f12370","tid":1804291,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:01:53.000Z","msg":"老手應該去黃店區，邊間無人就去邊間"},{"pid":"c085e2ffc007edd84ba3b9499fc674b12192a699","tid":1804291,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e79b0e29eb27d46d2796885265cd478bae17e20","tid":1804291,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:58:28.000Z","msg":"都係睇區內有邊間黃店<br />\n間間都試下 順便自己心入面俾分<br />\n有文宣會加 用支那寶會減<br />\n嘢食好唔好食 服務點樣<br />\n唔會特別幫襯死一間<br />\n利申：好憎排隊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上見有人想搞聯盟<br />\n我希望唔好搞大台<br />\n我覺得應該由每區內黃店自己組<br />\n組完可能做啲合作聯乘優惠互相推廣<br />\n而唔係我地好似有人逼佢地要點做"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:02:32.000Z","msg":"有d 區真係特別少, 太古得個2間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a315bd1c21127cd869bc5d5f89f058e2ce6e37a","tid":1804291,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:03:06.000Z","msg":"仲有黃色經濟圈，唔係黃色飲食圈"}]}